{"TopicId":131871,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Any way to change default flag without starting new game?","CreatedByName":"Elway358","CreatedById":157334,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-11T14:28:02Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Elway358","CreatedById":157334,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-11T14:28:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMornin\u0027 everyone. I made myself a few flags to use and everything went easy and they can be used inside the building facilities for missions. I am wondering if there is a way to reset one of them as my default flag without restarting a new save to get that flag selection window again? Thanks in advance for any help \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-02-11T14:31:26Z\u0022 title=\u002202/11/2016 02:31  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 11, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Elway358\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ketatrypt","CreatedById":157561,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-11T14:30:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nClick on the flagpole when you are in the facility overview screen. its clickable like any other building. Actually I just found this out a few days ago accidentally \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Elway358","CreatedById":157334,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-11T14:34:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222403703\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022131871\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221455201016\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022157561\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ketatrypt\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Ketatrypt said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nClick on the flagpole when you are in the facility overview screen. its clickable like any other building. Actually I just found this out a few days ago accidentally \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nD\u0027oh! I never even thought to try clicking the flag. Thanks very much! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}